{
  "manifest_version": "2",
  "task_list": [
    {
      "name": "Convert nd2 to OME-Zarr",
      "category": "Conversion",
      "tags": [
        "Nikon",
        "ND2",
        "Converter"
      ],
      "docs_info": "### Purpose\n- Convert a Nikon .nd2 file, or a folder of .nd2 files to an OME-Zarr file or plate.\n\n### Outputs\n- An OME-Zarr image or plate.\n\n### Limitations\n- This task has been tested on a limited set of acquisitions (see https://zenodo.org/records/15411420). It may not work on all Nikon .nd2 acquisitions.\n\n### Expected inputs\nThe following input layouts are supported. (The names in curly braces `{}` can be freely chosen by the user.)\n\n- Single file acquisition\n\t- acquisition path input:\n\t\t```text\n\t\t.../{filename}.nd2\n\t\t```\n\t- output: single OME-Zarr image\n\n- Folder of single file acquisitions\n\t- acquisition path input:\n\t\t```text\n\t\t.../{folder}\n\t\t----/{filename1}.nd2\n\t\t----/{filename2}.nd2\n\t\t...\n\t\t```\n\t- output: multiple OME-Zarr images\n\n- Folder of nd2 files belonging to a plate acquisitions\n\t- acquisition path input:\n\t\t```text\n\t\t.../{folder}\n\t\t----/WellA01{filename1}.nd2\n\t\t----/WellC02{filename2}.nd2\n\t\t...\n\t\t```\n\t- output: OME-Zarr plate\n\t- Note:\n\t\t- This works for files generated with the standard plate acquisition JOBS script at the ZMB Nikon Spinning Disk\n\t\t- The filenames MUST start with `Well` and the well name. Valid options for well names are e.g. `A1`, `A01`\n\t\t- If there are other .nd2 files in the folder that do not adhere to this, individual OME-Zarr images will be created instead of a plate\n\t\t- Splitting the positions into multiple files is NOT supported at the moment. (e.g. filenames like `WellB02_PointB02_0000_{filename}.nd2`)\n",
      "type": "converter_compound",
      "executable_non_parallel": "convert_nd2_init_task.py",
      "executable_parallel": "convert_nd2_compute_task.py",
      "meta_non_parallel": {
        "cpus_per_task": 1,
        "mem": 4000
      },
      "meta_parallel": {
        "cpus_per_task": 1,
        "mem": 12000
      },
      "args_schema_non_parallel": {
        "$defs": {
          "AdvancedComputeOptions": {
            "description": "Advanced options for the conversion.",
            "properties": {
              "num_levels": {
                "default": 5,
                "minimum": 1,
                "title": "Num Levels",
                "type": "integer"
              },
              "tiling_mode": {
                "default": "auto",
                "enum": [
                  "auto",
                  "grid",
                  "free",
                  "none"
                ],
                "title": "Tiling Mode",
                "type": "string"
              },
              "swap_xy": {
                "default": false,
                "title": "Swap Xy",
                "type": "boolean"
              },
              "invert_x": {
                "default": false,
                "title": "Invert X",
                "type": "boolean"
              },
              "invert_y": {
                "default": false,
                "title": "Invert Y",
                "type": "boolean"
              },
              "max_xy_chunk": {
                "default": 4096,
                "minimum": 1,
                "title": "Max Xy Chunk",
                "type": "integer"
              },
              "z_chunk": {
                "default": 10,
                "minimum": 1,
                "title": "Z Chunk",
                "type": "integer"
              },
              "c_chunk": {
                "default": 1,
                "minimum": 1,
                "title": "C Chunk",
                "type": "integer"
              },
              "t_chunk": {
                "default": 1,
                "minimum": 1,
                "title": "T Chunk",
                "type": "integer"
              }
            },
            "title": "AdvancedComputeOptions",
            "type": "object"
          },
          "Nd2InputModel": {
            "description": "Acquisition metadata.",
            "properties": {
              "path": {
                "title": "Path",
                "type": "string"
              },
              "plate_name": {
                "title": "Plate Name",
                "type": "string"
              },
              "acquisition_id": {
                "default": 0,
                "minimum": 0,
                "title": "Acquisition Id",
                "type": "integer"
              }
            },
            "required": [
              "path"
            ],
            "title": "Nd2InputModel",
            "type": "object"
          }
        },
        "additionalProperties": false,
        "properties": {
          "zarr_dir": {
            "title": "Zarr Dir",
            "type": "string",
            "description": "Directory to store the Zarr files."
          },
          "acquisitions": {
            "items": {
              "$ref": "#/$defs/Nd2InputModel"
            },
            "title": "Acquisitions",
            "type": "array",
            "description": "List of raw acquisitions to convert to OME-Zarr."
          },
          "overwrite": {
            "default": false,
            "title": "Overwrite",
            "type": "boolean",
            "description": "Overwrite existing Zarr files."
          },
          "advanced_options": {
            "$ref": "#/$defs/AdvancedComputeOptions",
            "default": {
              "num_levels": 5,
              "tiling_mode": "auto",
              "swap_xy": false,
              "invert_x": false,
              "invert_y": false,
              "max_xy_chunk": 4096,
              "z_chunk": 10,
              "c_chunk": 1,
              "t_chunk": 1
            },
            "title": "Advanced Options",
            "description": "Advanced options for the conversion."
          }
        },
        "required": [
          "zarr_dir",
          "acquisitions"
        ],
        "type": "object",
        "title": "ConvertNd2InitTask"
